FDA - Adverse Event Reporting System (FAERS) 
FOIA Case Report Information
A the time of death, it was not known whether the therapy with rituximab was ongoing or not.
The physician did not report a causality between fatal progressive multifocal leukoencephalopathy and rituximab.
No further information was provided
The French imputability concerning the event fatal progressive multifocal leukoencephalopathy  and rituximab is 
